---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Servicios | MyAllSupport | IRIS Solutions">
  <style>
    .service-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.26);
      transition: transform 140ms ease, box-shadow 140ms ease, border-color 140ms ease, background 140ms ease;
    }
    .service-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      border-color: rgba(125,211,252,0.55);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.32);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(125,211,252,0.18), rgba(167,139,250,0.10));
    }
  </style>

  <section class="card service-card" style="padding: 16px; border-radius: 22px;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Servicios sobre InterSystems IRIS</h1>
    <p class="muted" style="margin:0; line-height:1.7;">
      Enfoque “rápido y comprobable”: PoCs breves, alto impacto, y ruta clara a producción.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 12px; display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 12px;">
    <div class="card service-card" style="padding: 14px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 6px;">PoC (2–4 semanas)</h2>
      <ul class="muted" style="margin:0; line-height:1.75;">
        <li>Definición de caso de uso + criterios de éxito</li>
        <li>Demo funcional + arquitectura + backlog</li>
        <li>Repo + documentación + plan de escalamiento</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card service-card" style="padding: 14px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Integración & Interop</h2>
      <ul class="muted" style="margin:0; line-height:1.75;">
        <li>SAP / JDBC / APIs / Webhooks</li>
        <li>Productions, retries, monitoreo y trazabilidad</li>
        <li>Hardening y operación</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card service-card" style="padding: 14px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Analytics & ML</h2>
      <ul class="muted" style="margin:0; line-height:1.75;">
        <li>Modelos dimensionales / Cubos</li>
        <li>IntegratedML aplicado al flujo operacional</li>
        <li>Gobierno de datos + seguridad</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
